  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of an eight-hour version of
      Reducing the Risk on outcomes such as sexual initiation, condom and contraceptive use, number
      of sexual partners, and pregnancy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
